      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $z_0,z_1,\\dots,z_n \\in \\C$ tels que :\n$\\forall\\ P \\in \\C_{n-1}[X]$, on a $P(z_0) = \\frac {P(z_1) +\\dots+ P(z_n)}n$.\n\\\\\nOn note $\\Phi(X) = \\prod_{i=1}^n (X-z_i)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_0,z_1,\\dots,z_n \\in \\C\\)</span>\ntels que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ P \\in\n\\C_{n-1}[X]\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P(z_0) = \\frac\n{P(z_1) +\\dots+ P(z_n)}n\\)</span>.<br />\nOn note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Phi(X) = \\prod_{i=1}^n\n(X-z_i)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d03418f0-6d77-401b-bd06-62003e47e5b5",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac\n{\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16498637-83a9-4303-8c5e-a70ed691d5e4",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P = \\frac \\Phi{X-z_k}  \\Rightarrow \n     \\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}  = \\frac {\\Phi'(z_k)}n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P = \\frac \\Phi{X-z_k}  \\Rightarrow\n     \\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}  = \\frac {\\Phi&#39;(z_k)}n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d43665d9-d0aa-48a0-99ab-f380fab7bb9e",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que $\\Phi(X) = \\frac {(X-z_0)\\Phi'(X)}n + \\Phi(z_0)$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Phi(X) =\n\\frac {(X-z_0)\\Phi&#39;(X)}n + \\Phi(z_0)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
